    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double VANOS system to achieve a breathtaking 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained with documented rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's known longitudinal stress points. The suspension retains its factory-correct kinematics, and the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering provides the unfiltered feedback expected of a true driver's machine. Mechanically flawless and cosmetically impeccable, this is an investment-grade example of BMW\u2019s finest M-division era.",
