      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality specimen, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the factory scent persists, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records documenting every scheduled maintenance interval. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
